== Audio

These look like buttons, but are not:
{btn:.r 440}
{btn:.g 528}
{btn:.b 660}
{btn: 1000}

This plays 1kHz:
{btn-sine: 1000}

These play a minor triad:
{btn-sine:.r.toggle 440}
{btn-sine:.g.toggle 528}
{btn-sine:.b.toggle 660}

With text:
{btn-sine:.r.toggle a|440}
{btn-sine:.g.toggle c|528}
{btn-sine:.b.toggle e|660}